    Description
    AbstractLampEvent
    The abstract class AbstractLampEvent enforces a common type for all lamp simulation events.
    DecreaseLamp
    The class DecreaseLamp defines the simulation event of the Cooking Plate being decreased to a lower temperature mode.
    IncreaseLamp
    The class IncreaseLamp defines the simulation event of the Cooking Plate being increased to high temperature mode.
    SwitchOffLamp
    The class SwitchOffLamp defines the simulation event of the lamp being switched off.
    SwitchOnLamp
    The class SwitchOnLamp defines the simulation event of the lamp being switched On.
